42
00:02:55,790 --> 00:02:57,490
Hope Huaiji is well.

43
00:02:58,420 --> 00:02:59,540
Don’t get hurt.

44
00:03:04,460 --> 00:03:05,220
Your Majesty.

45
00:03:06,020 --> 00:03:08,020
From the sound and the fire,

46
