60
00:03:29,100 --> 00:03:30,580
But you must protect His Majesty.

61
00:03:32,980 --> 00:03:33,900
Yes, Your Highness.

62
00:03:34,220 --> 00:03:36,980
I apologize for my recklessness.

63
00:03:38,780 --> 00:03:39,460
Shouzhong.

64
00:03:42,820 --> 00:03:43,540
Your Majesty.

65
00:03:44,220 --> 00:03:45,620
The culprits don’t come in,

66
00:03:45,860 --> 00:03:46,940
