98
00:05:10,740 --> 00:05:11,820
When the rebellion is suppressed,

99
00:05:12,140 --> 00:05:13,260
I’ll award you

100
00:05:13,900 --> 00:05:14,860
and your hair that I cut

101
00:05:14,860 --> 00:05:16,100
