108
00:06:22,020 --> 00:06:23,380
We don’t know whether it’s rebellion.

109
00:06:23,740 --> 00:06:24,900
I don’t dare to let you go.

110
00:06:24,940 --> 00:06:26,140
I also don’t know where His Majesty is.

111
00:06:27,420 --> 00:06:28,540
You don’t know whether it’s rebellion.

112
00:06:29,420 --> 00:06:30,540
I have one more reason to go.

113
00:06:31,300 --> 00:06:32,460
- Madam Zhang. - Madam Zhang.

114
00:06:33,020 --> 00:06:34,300
- Madam Zhang. - Madam Zhang.

115
00:06:35,700 --> 00:06:36,740
You guys, follow me.

116
00:06:38,140 --> 00:06:38,860
Hurry up.

117
00:07:05,340 --> 00:07:07,100
Deputy Officer Zhang will go with you.

118
00:07:08,140 --> 00:07:10,220
Follow his order.

119
00:07:11,500 --> 00:07:12,260
Deputy Officer Zhang.

120
00:07:12,620 --> 00:07:13,300
Yes.

121
00:07:16,100 --> 00:07:16,860
Qiuhe is smart.

122
00:07:18,060 --> 00:07:19,180
She can give you suggestion.

123
00:07:19,900 --> 00:07:20,460
Yes.

124
00:07:21,620 --> 00:07:23,820
