129
00:07:48,220 --> 00:07:48,940
Danshu.

130
00:07:53,980 --> 00:07:55,140
Let’s have a tea competition.

131
00:08:02,100 --> 00:08:02,780
OK.

132
00:08:17,180 --> 00:08:18,020
I lost.

133
00:08:19,060 --> 00:08:20,260
You are not calm.

134
00:08:33,060 --> 00:08:35,140
I thought you pretended to be calm,

135
00:08:36,300 --> 00:08:38,060
