138
00:08:52,060 --> 00:08:53,580
The worst result is that I die.

139
00:08:53,620 --> 00:08:55,420
Don’t say these unlucky words.

140
00:08:59,940 --> 00:09:00,980
If I

141
00:09:01,100 --> 00:09:02,660
die with you,

142
00:09:02,700 --> 00:09:04,380
I have no regret, so I’m not afraid.

143
00:09:05,020 --> 00:09:07,460
