144
00:09:12,140 --> 00:09:13,980
I would like to die for you.

145
00:09:18,020 --> 00:09:18,780
I know.

146
00:09:23,020 --> 00:09:24,860
Our country will still be fine without me.

147
00:09:26,220 --> 00:09:27,940
But it can’t lose you.

148
00:09:29,420 --> 00:09:30,180
Now...

149
00:09:30,180 --> 00:09:32,980
Now, I haven’t had crown prince.

150
00:09:36,380 --> 00:09:37,420
Don’t worry.

151
00:09:38,500 --> 00:09:40,100
I don’t have biological sons.

152
00:09:40,100 --> 00:09:41,260
And I have chronic disease.

153
00:09:42,140 --> 00:09:43,860
So I have planned everything well.

154
00:09:45,820 --> 00:09:46,620
Your Majesty.

155
00:09:47,380 --> 00:09:48,340
I don’t mean...

156
00:09:48,540 --> 00:09:49,260
Alright.

157
00:09:49,700 --> 00:09:50,500
I know.

158
00:09:52,740 --> 00:09:53,380
Who is it?

159
00:09:55,700 --> 00:09:57,500
Mr. Zhang, it’s me.

160
00:09:57,940 --> 00:09:59,140
Madam Zhang is here.

161
00:10:06,100 --> 00:10:07,380
Please let her in.

162
00:10:32,220 --> 00:10:33,460
Send her to treatment.

163
00:10:33,460 --> 00:10:34,220
-Yes. -Yes.

164
00:10:41,220 --> 00:10:42,020
I think the culprits

165
00:10:43,060 --> 00:10:44,260
