166
00:10:47,260 --> 00:10:49,420
Do you still have firecrackers

167
00:10:49,580 --> 00:10:50,980
prepared for the Hall of Happiness
and Tranquility last month?

168
00:10:52,620 --> 00:10:53,700
Yes. I’ll go to get them.

169
00:10:53,940 --> 00:10:54,580
Hurry up.

170
00:11:22,940 --> 00:11:23,860
There’s no sound inside.

171
00:11:25,540 --> 00:11:26,540
Firecrackers are here.

172
00:12:02,940 --> 00:12:03,860
Tell me,

173
00:12:03,860 --> 00:12:04,940
we need someone alive for interrogation.

174
00:12:06,140 --> 00:12:06,740
I...

175
00:12:07,340 --> 00:12:08,740
I just left for a while.

176
00:12:08,940 --> 00:12:09,500
How...

177
00:12:09,580 --> 00:12:10,940
How did madam disappear?

178
00:12:12,580 --> 00:12:13,580
You have many people.

179
00:12:13,660 --> 00:12:14,220
How come...

180
00:12:14,220 --> 00:12:16,340
How come you let her leave?

181
00:12:16,940 --> 00:12:17,900
What should I do?

182
00:12:17,940 --> 00:12:18,860
Go to find her.

183
00:12:18,900 --> 00:12:20,220
Go.

184
00:12:20,260 --> 00:12:21,340
All the eunuchs of the Pavilion of Luan

185
00:12:21,340 --> 00:12:22,780
went to find her, aunt.

186
00:12:23,020 --> 00:12:24,260
I mean all of you go to find her.

187
00:12:24,260 --> 00:12:25,660
Go now!

188
00:12:25,660 --> 00:12:26,660
Go!

189
00:12:26,660 --> 00:12:27,300
Aunt.

190
00:12:28,060 --> 00:12:28,780
We found her.

191
00:12:28,860 --> 00:12:29,580
We found her.

192
00:12:29,700 --> 00:12:30,980
Madam is at the Hall of Peace.

193
00:12:32,140 --> 00:12:33,060
Hall of Peace?

194
00:12:33,420 --> 00:12:34,060
Yes.

195
00:12:34,380 --> 00:12:35,380
Madam is at the Hall of Peace.

196
00:12:35,660 --> 00:12:36,460
His Majesty is also there.

197
00:12:37,820 --> 00:12:39,180
His... His Majesty is also there?

198
00:12:47,860 --> 00:12:49,420
Don’t be afraid.

199
00:12:50,260 --> 00:12:51,820
The physician can’t come now.

200
00:12:52,580 --> 00:12:53,940
But Maoze can acupuncture you.

201
00:12:54,460 --> 00:12:55,540
Maoze is professional at medicine.

202
00:12:57,140 --> 00:12:58,060
Don’t worry.

203
00:13:01,180 --> 00:13:02,140
You are here with me.

204
00:13:03,300 --> 00:13:04,380
I’m not afraid.

205
00:13:08,980 --> 00:13:10,380
I couldn’t stop Madam Zhang.

206
00:13:11,020 --> 00:13:11,980
I didn’t dare to force her.

207
00:13:12,420 --> 00:13:13,380
So I just followed her.

208
00:13:14,740 --> 00:13:17,180
Madam Zhang almost lost her mind.

209
00:13:18,020 --> 00:13:19,300
She fell down several times

210
00:13:19,940 --> 00:13:22,220
and was hurt by stones and bushes.

211
00:13:23,140 --> 00:13:24,420
Also, her asthma attacked.

212
00:13:25,540 --> 00:13:27,380
After I agreed to find His Majesty with her,

213
00:13:28,100 --> 00:13:30,100
