214
00:13:31,700 --> 00:13:33,220
I wanted to waste some time on our way.

215
00:13:34,140 --> 00:13:35,580
But we saw

216
00:13:35,580 --> 00:13:37,020
some eunuchs with weapons

217
00:13:37,500 --> 00:13:38,740
going to the Hall of Happiness and Tranquility,

218
00:13:39,820 --> 00:13:41,100
and Chief of Styling Dong was among them.

219
00:13:42,220 --> 00:13:43,340
So Madam Zhang said

220
00:13:43,980 --> 00:13:45,260
that His Majesty was at the Hall of Peace.

221
00:13:47,100 --> 00:13:48,900
We haven’t known who the culprits are.

222
00:13:50,380 --> 00:13:51,020
How can you be sure

223
00:13:51,020 --> 00:13:52,580
that they won’t follow you

224
00:13:52,580 --> 00:13:53,580
