225
00:13:58,540 --> 00:13:59,660
I deserve to die.

226
00:14:00,500 --> 00:14:01,580
Please punish me.

227
00:14:03,620 --> 00:14:04,340
Bihan.

228
00:14:05,700 --> 00:14:06,380
Bihan.

229
00:14:11,620 --> 00:14:12,340
Your Majesty,

230
00:14:12,540 --> 00:14:15,300
please let me diagnose and treat Madam Zhang.

231
00:14:24,580 --> 00:14:26,380
You are His Majesty’s favorite eunuch

232
00:14:27,140 --> 00:14:28,780
who knows what he thinks the best.

233
00:14:29,740 --> 00:14:30,860
His Majesty will decide

234
00:14:31,700 --> 00:14:32,700
whether you are guilty.

235
00:14:37,380 --> 00:14:38,140
Your Highness,

236
00:14:38,860 --> 00:14:40,380
they killed the culprits

237
00:14:40,700 --> 00:14:41,540
and came back.

238
00:14:47,100 --> 00:14:48,300
There were only four men,

239
00:14:48,460 --> 00:14:49,460
full of the smell of liquor.

240
00:14:49,460 --> 00:14:50,380
Seemed that they were drunk.

241
00:14:50,580 --> 00:14:51,420
They couldn’t stand steadily

242
00:14:51,420 --> 00:14:52,340
and were muddled.

243
00:14:52,540 --> 00:14:54,300
We have many more people,

244
00:14:54,620 --> 00:14:56,340
so three of them were killed immediately.

245
00:14:56,500 --> 00:14:57,460
One escaped.

246
00:14:57,540 --> 00:14:58,780
I sent men

247
00:14:58,860 --> 00:14:59,860
to strongly search.

248
00:15:00,580 --> 00:15:02,100
Did you know their identities?

249
00:15:02,500 --> 00:15:04,420
The fight was too fierce.

250
00:15:05,100 --> 00:15:06,500
After our sticks,

251
00:15:06,820 --> 00:15:08,380
the three’s bodies were badly mutilated,

252
00:15:08,380 --> 00:15:09,220
which it’s hard to find their identities.

253
00:15:09,740 --> 00:15:11,300
But we searched their bodies

254
00:15:11,300 --> 00:15:13,500
and found their badges and other belongings.

255
00:15:51,100 --> 00:15:52,880
Yan Xiu, Guo Kui and Sun Li

256
00:15:52,900 --> 00:15:53,770
were killed.

257
00:15:54,060 --> 00:15:55,300
= From Cailing =
Wang Sheng escaped under the chaos.

258
00:15:55,310 --> 00:15:56,310
I’ve ordered all the departments

259
00:15:56,310 --> 00:15:57,090
to search carefully.

260
00:16:12,660 --> 00:16:13,700
Take Yuan Cailing

261
00:16:13,940 --> 00:16:14,860
to the hall.

262
00:16:54,320 --> 00:16:55,680
Are these scholars

263
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:57,160
good ones?

264
00:16:58,100 --> 00:16:59,300
Ouyang Xiu

265
00:16:59,300 --> 00:17:00,620
coveted his nephew,

266
00:17:00,620 --> 00:17:01,700
which can be proved by lewd poems.

267
00:17:02,460 --> 00:17:03,700
Cui Bai

268
00:17:04,820 --> 00:17:06,300
drew the Incense Making Painting,

269
00:17:06,300 --> 00:17:07,940
which was popular among the public.

270
00:17:08,340 --> 00:17:10,380
A maid was highlighted in this painting.

271
00:17:11,100 --> 00:17:12,220
Everyone thinks

272
00:17:12,460 --> 00:17:14,180
this maid is someone that the painter admires.

273
00:17:15,340 --> 00:17:16,940
The makeup

274
00:17:17,060 --> 00:17:18,020
of that maid

275
00:17:18,020 --> 00:17:19,620
was well-received in the Capital for a while.

276
00:17:20,060 --> 00:17:21,220
I didn’t find that the maid

277
00:17:21,740 --> 00:17:23,660
is Dong Qiuhe, who’s the Empress’s favorite maid

278
00:17:23,740 --> 00:17:26,540
until today.

279
00:17:28,820 --> 00:17:30,780
But nobody knows whether he admires her

280
00:17:31,060 --> 00:17:32,900
or has amour with her.

281
00:17:36,700 --> 00:17:37,500
= Yuan Cailing =
Your Highness.

282
00:17:38,260 --> 00:17:39,460
I never collude with them.

283
00:17:39,460 --> 00:17:40,580
I don’t know.

284
00:17:40,660 --> 00:17:42,100
I know nothing about it.

285
00:17:49,340 --> 00:17:50,740
This letter is written by you.

286
00:17:51,660 --> 00:17:54,700
How dare you ask the culprit

287
00:17:54,700 --> 00:17:55,780
to meet at a certain time and place?

288
00:17:56,740 --> 00:18:00,460
You must have colluded with him for long.

289
00:18:02,540 --> 00:18:03,660
For these months,

290
00:18:04,660 --> 00:18:06,860
you didn’t show up

291
00:18:06,900 --> 00:18:08,700
with the reason that you got cold.

292
00:18:10,620 --> 00:18:12,100
You really know nothing?

293
00:18:12,740 --> 00:18:13,500
Your Highness.

294
00:18:13,860 --> 00:18:15,100
Last year,

295
00:18:15,300 --> 00:18:17,660
I met Yan Xiu outside the Hall of Polities.

296
00:18:18,220 --> 00:18:19,380
I was stupid

297
00:18:19,860 --> 00:18:20,860
and seduced by him.

298
00:18:21,500 --> 00:18:22,860
But I didn’t think

299
00:18:23,020 --> 00:18:25,300
he could do such a thing.

300
00:18:25,460 --> 00:18:26,260
Your Highness.

301
00:18:27,420 --> 00:18:29,340
Though you didn’t know that

302
00:18:29,340 --> 00:18:30,300
Yan Xiu is a culprit,

303
00:18:32,100 --> 00:18:33,620
it’s a serious offense

304
00:18:33,620 --> 00:18:34,580
that you have affairs with an Imperial Guard.

305
00:18:37,340 --> 00:18:38,540
You should be sentenced to death under the law.

306
00:18:45,540 --> 00:18:46,940
Laws and rules are the most important

307
00:18:48,020 --> 00:18:49,740
in Your Highness’s eyes.

308
00:18:51,660 --> 00:18:53,020
So, Your Highness must

309
00:18:53,500 --> 00:18:54,860
be more serious to servants of Hall of Peace.

310
00:18:56,060 --> 00:18:58,180
How come the maid serving Your Highness

311
00:18:58,180 --> 00:18:59,940
for many years

312
00:19:00,220 --> 00:19:01,300
has affair with an Imperial Guard?

313
00:19:03,220 --> 00:19:04,900
It really shocks me.

314
00:19:05,940 --> 00:19:07,580
It’s cold here. You are still weak.

315
00:19:07,900 --> 00:19:09,060
You should have a rest.

316
00:19:09,140 --> 00:19:10,100
Why did you go out?

317
00:19:10,620 --> 00:19:11,420
Go back.

318
00:19:12,020 --> 00:19:12,980
Your Majesty.

319
00:19:13,980 --> 00:19:15,220
This is not the Pavilion of Luan.

320
00:19:16,220 --> 00:19:18,140
I don’t want to stay inside alone.

321
00:19:25,620 --> 00:19:26,340
Here.

322
00:19:42,860 --> 00:19:44,940
I can’t believe

323
00:19:44,940 --> 00:19:46,220
a maid who’s been serving the Empress for years

324
00:19:46,260 --> 00:19:47,260
has an affair with an Imperial Guard,

325
00:19:48,020 --> 00:19:49,660
which brought this disaster.

326
00:19:51,260 --> 00:19:52,100
I wonder

327
00:19:53,620 --> 00:19:55,260
if there are similar cases

328
00:19:55,540 --> 00:19:58,380
that haven’t been noticed.

329
00:20:12,620 --> 00:20:13,340
Your Majesty,

330
00:20:14,060 --> 00:20:15,540
when I ordered that no one

331
00:20:15,540 --> 00:20:16,540
could stay where he or she is,

332
00:20:16,860 --> 00:20:18,140
you didn’t object, did you?

333
00:20:23,660 --> 00:20:24,700
Can the Pavilion of Luan

334
00:20:25,180 --> 00:20:27,740
disobey the Empress’s order?

335
00:20:47,500 --> 00:20:48,540
What’s happening outside?

336
00:20:49,660 --> 00:20:50,340
It is said

337
00:20:50,780 --> 00:20:52,060
that the culprits were killed.

338
00:20:52,340 --> 00:20:53,100
It’s peaceful now.

339
00:20:53,620 --> 00:20:54,620
They were all killed?

340
00:20:54,980 --> 00:20:56,060
They said one escaped.

341
00:20:56,260 --> 00:20:57,500
How could they let him escape?

342
00:21:00,060 --> 00:21:01,060
What should we do?

343
00:21:02,220 --> 00:21:02,940
Go.

344
00:21:03,220 --> 00:21:04,020
Go to investigate

345
00:21:04,020 --> 00:21:05,620
who went to catch the culprits.

346
00:21:05,660 --> 00:21:06,540
Hurry up. No!

347
00:21:07,540 --> 00:21:08,420
Go to the Imperial Security Agency

348
00:21:08,660 --> 00:21:10,260
and tell Deputy Officer Yang

349
00:21:10,260 --> 00:21:10,900
that

350
00:21:10,900 --> 00:21:11,740
a culprit escaped.

351
00:21:12,060 --> 00:21:12,820
Hurry to go.

352
00:21:13,060 --> 00:21:14,620
Deputy Officer Yang

353
00:21:15,020 --> 00:21:16,900
is on duty tonight,

354
00:21:17,020 --> 00:21:18,980
and it’s him who took people to search.

355
00:21:22,780 --> 00:21:23,460
That’s fine.

356
00:21:23,860 --> 00:21:24,740
That’s fine.

357
00:22:35,320 --> 00:22:36,760
In my heart, His Majesty

358
00:22:37,040 --> 00:22:38,240
is more important than my life.

359
00:22:39,760 --> 00:22:41,600
I must know whether His Majesty is safe.

360
00:22:42,440 --> 00:22:44,320
The order can’t stop me.

361
00:22:48,480 --> 00:22:49,160
Now,

362
00:22:50,520 --> 00:22:52,120
I know that His Majesty is in safety.

363
00:22:53,040 --> 00:22:54,880
But I don’t regret that I broke the order.

364
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:57,240
I’m waiting for the punishment.

365
00:23:05,000 --> 00:23:05,880
I thought about it.

366
00:23:07,680 --> 00:23:10,480
I stayed in the Hall of Peace.

367
00:23:11,960 --> 00:23:15,040
If Ling’er tried to commit treason with Yan Xiu,

368
00:23:16,040 --> 00:23:17,920
these culprits must have got information earlier.

369
00:23:18,240 --> 00:23:19,760
They wouldn’t have set on fire
in the Hall of Happiness and Tranquility.

370
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:21,880
Also,

371
00:23:23,560 --> 00:23:24,960
she’s a maid close to the Empress.

372
00:23:25,560 --> 00:23:27,320
If she attempted to hurt me,

373
00:23:27,720 --> 00:23:28,720
she has a lot of chances.

374
00:23:29,080 --> 00:23:31,160
They don’t need to do this today.

375
00:23:33,400 --> 00:23:34,280
It’s wise of you, Your Majesty.

376
00:23:34,680 --> 00:23:36,400
I was just confused.

377
00:23:36,480 --> 00:23:37,920
How can I commit treason?

378
00:23:38,240 --> 00:23:39,800
Please don’t sentence me to death.

379
00:23:44,920 --> 00:23:45,800
If it’s clear

380
00:23:46,360 --> 00:23:48,040
that she isn’t one of the culprits,

381
00:23:49,040 --> 00:23:50,880
she’ll be forgiven

382
00:23:51,280 --> 00:23:53,120
since she’s been serving you for years.

383
00:23:53,920 --> 00:23:55,800
Also, she’s at an age to have marriage,

384
00:23:56,880 --> 00:23:59,560
but she didn’t meet a right one.

385
00:24:01,120 --> 00:24:02,000
His Majesty is right.

386
00:24:03,360 --> 00:24:04,120
What’s more,

387
00:24:05,520 --> 00:24:06,840
maybe more maids

388
00:24:06,840 --> 00:24:07,800
have broken our rules

389
00:24:08,040 --> 00:24:09,480
and colluded with men.

390
00:24:10,760 --> 00:24:11,720
After I go back,

391
00:24:12,040 --> 00:24:12,760
I’ll completely investigate

392
00:24:12,760 --> 00:24:14,000
the servants in the Pavilion of Luan.

393
00:24:14,320 --> 00:24:15,160
Bihan,

394
00:24:16,360 --> 00:24:17,720
I am dealing with the issue

395
00:24:17,840 --> 00:24:18,920
of the Hall of Peace with the Empress.

396
00:24:19,280 --> 00:24:20,400
It’s nothing to do with the Pavilion of Luan.

397
00:24:23,720 --> 00:24:24,920
Huaiji, get the sedan chair ready.

398
00:24:25,600 --> 00:24:27,000
Send Madam Zhang back.

399
00:24:28,800 --> 00:24:29,440
Yes.

400
00:24:36,240 --> 00:24:37,320
Go back and have a good rest.

401
00:24:37,720 --> 00:24:40,000
The Empress and I will send

402
00:24:40,000 --> 00:24:40,840
an Imperial Physician to the Pavilion of Luan.

403
00:25:10,840 --> 00:25:11,720
Take care of Madam Zhang.

404
00:25:28,840 --> 00:25:29,920
Huirou, where are you going?

405
00:25:31,560 --> 00:25:32,280
Mother,

406
00:25:32,600 --> 00:25:33,760
I’m worried about father.

407
00:25:33,760 --> 00:25:34,840
I need to go to see him.

408
00:25:35,520 --> 00:25:37,560
We can’t go out of here under the order
from Her Highness.

409
00:25:37,680 --> 00:25:39,080
We must stay here

410
00:25:39,080 --> 00:25:40,600
until a new order is issued.

411
00:25:41,080 --> 00:25:41,800
But

412
00:25:41,960 --> 00:25:43,520
what if father is in danger?

413
00:25:44,120 --> 00:25:45,320
Even if he’s in danger,

414
00:25:45,320 --> 00:25:46,120
can you fight against the culprits

415
00:25:46,160 --> 00:25:47,720
to protect him?

416
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:50,160
I can stay with him.

417
00:25:50,920 --> 00:25:52,080
Madam. Princess.

418
00:25:55,040 --> 00:25:56,000
Madam. Princess.

419
00:25:56,160 --> 00:25:57,640
I checked at the yard just now,

420
00:25:58,120 --> 00:25:59,960
and I found this letter.

421
00:26:05,280 --> 00:26:06,440
The culprits were killed.

422
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:08,040
His Majesty is safe.

423
00:26:08,280 --> 00:26:09,320
Princess, don’t worry.

424
00:26:09,960 --> 00:26:11,080
Is this real?

425
00:26:14,720 --> 00:26:15,640
This is real!

426
00:26:15,960 --> 00:26:17,240
It was written by Huaiji.

427
00:26:18,680 --> 00:26:19,880
I can’t tell it wrongly.

428
00:26:20,640 --> 00:26:22,120
Huaiji knows that I’m worried about father,

429
00:26:22,240 --> 00:26:23,960
so he makes me rest assured.

430
00:26:24,840 --> 00:26:26,440
Thank goodness.

431
00:26:26,760 --> 00:26:28,280
Huaiji is really a good kid,

432
00:26:28,880 --> 00:26:30,200
smart and considerate.

433
00:26:31,640 --> 00:26:33,720
Huaiji is the best man.

434
00:26:46,360 --> 00:26:47,400
Your Majesty,

435
00:26:47,880 --> 00:26:49,200
the Imperial Security Agency tried their best

436
00:26:49,200 --> 00:26:50,280
to seize the culprit, Wang Sheng.

437
00:26:50,640 --> 00:26:52,240
I also searched their residences.

438
00:26:52,440 --> 00:26:53,840
All their things have been locked.

439
00:26:54,440 --> 00:26:56,680
We didn’t find any letter about treason.

440
00:26:58,040 --> 00:26:58,920
But,

441
00:26:59,840 --> 00:27:03,600
at Yan Xiu’s place, we found...

442
00:27:10,560 --> 00:27:12,040
We found some things

443
00:27:12,360 --> 00:27:14,160
from the Hall of Peace.

444
00:27:14,640 --> 00:27:16,000
And some letters...

445
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:19,200
I don’t dare to open.

446
00:27:22,840 --> 00:27:23,600
I...

447
00:27:24,280 --> 00:27:25,480
I didn’t...

448
00:27:25,960 --> 00:27:26,760
I just...

449
00:27:27,920 --> 00:27:28,560
I...

450
00:27:33,000 --> 00:27:33,840
Just now,

451
00:27:34,680 --> 00:27:35,960
I concluded

452
00:27:36,840 --> 00:27:39,440
that Yuan Cailing had an affair with the guard.

453
00:27:39,840 --> 00:27:41,360
But she didn’t attempt to commit treason.

454
00:27:42,760 --> 00:27:43,960
The things

455
00:27:43,960 --> 00:27:45,000
from the Hall of Peace

456
00:27:45,720 --> 00:27:48,320
must be girl’s personal belongings.

457
00:27:48,560 --> 00:27:49,600
And the letters

458
00:27:50,440 --> 00:27:52,560
must be full of frivolous and filthy words.

459
00:27:57,920 --> 00:27:58,680
Burn the parcel.

460
00:28:04,760 --> 00:28:06,680
Now that you didn’t find

461
00:28:06,920 --> 00:28:08,240
anything about treason,

462
00:28:08,640 --> 00:28:10,480
why did you bring these personal belongings?

463
00:28:12,040 --> 00:28:13,400
Do you want me to

464
00:28:13,640 --> 00:28:15,320
check them one by one with the Empress?

465
00:28:16,040 --> 00:28:17,240
Isn’t my image important?

466
00:28:19,800 --> 00:28:21,160
I am stupid.

467
00:28:26,320 --> 00:28:27,080
Forget it.

468
00:28:28,720 --> 00:28:29,760
I’ve been disturbed a whole night.

469
00:28:31,520 --> 00:28:33,040
It’s almost the time of the morning meeting.

470
00:28:38,600 --> 00:28:39,440
Danshu.

471
00:28:41,720 --> 00:28:44,400
Yuan Cailing had an affair with an Imperial Guard.

472
00:28:46,960 --> 00:28:48,120
She deserves to die based on the rule.

473
00:28:50,360 --> 00:28:51,720
However,

474
00:28:55,320 --> 00:28:57,760
the rule is made by humans.

475
00:28:58,160 --> 00:28:59,800
It can be flexible.

476
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:39,800
Chief Xia.

477
00:29:40,840 --> 00:29:41,640
Chief Xia.

478
00:29:42,800 --> 00:29:45,480
There was a chaos in the palace last night.

479
00:29:46,080 --> 00:29:47,080
Is His Majesty all right?

480
00:29:47,480 --> 00:29:48,360
Yes.

481
00:29:48,520 --> 00:29:49,320
It’s lucky.

482
00:29:49,720 --> 00:29:51,120
Were the culprits arrested?

483
00:29:51,120 --> 00:29:51,880
Who are they?

484
00:29:52,760 --> 00:29:53,720
I was just informed

485
00:29:53,720 --> 00:29:55,080
that they

486
00:29:55,600 --> 00:29:56,800
were not arrested.

487
00:29:57,720 --> 00:29:59,360
Some escaped and most were killed.

488
00:30:01,240 --> 00:30:02,760
But it’s weird

489
00:30:03,680 --> 00:30:05,520
that this disaster was brought

490
00:30:05,560 --> 00:30:07,680
by an amour between a maid and an Imperial Guard.

491
00:30:08,880 --> 00:30:10,840
The Empress always strictly obeys rules.

492
00:30:11,160 --> 00:30:12,760
How come it happened?

493
00:30:13,120 --> 00:30:14,160
So strange.

494
00:30:16,160 --> 00:30:17,560
It must be investigated seriously.

495
00:30:17,960 --> 00:30:19,480
Their accomplices must be erased.

496
00:31:05,400 --> 00:31:06,600
Maid Yuan Cailing

497
00:31:07,640 --> 00:31:08,920
had an affair with an Imperial Guard,

498
00:31:09,440 --> 00:31:10,560
which had broken the rules.

499
00:31:11,040 --> 00:31:12,240
She’s supposed to be sentenced to death.

500
00:31:14,080 --> 00:31:15,560
Your Majesty, please allow me

501
00:31:16,240 --> 00:31:19,160
to execute her under the rules.

502
00:31:26,560 --> 00:31:27,880
Ling’er was cautious.

503
00:31:28,760 --> 00:31:30,640
I don’t know she made any mistake.

504
00:31:32,080 --> 00:31:34,040
This time, she’s careless.

505
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:36,080
How about beating her

506
00:31:36,320 --> 00:31:37,640
thirty times

507
00:31:38,360 --> 00:31:39,280
and driving her out of the palace?

508
00:31:39,920 --> 00:31:40,960
This punishment is enough.

509
00:31:43,120 --> 00:31:46,880
But her carelessness brought a disaster
to the palace.

510
00:31:48,320 --> 00:31:49,960
Many eunuchs are injured,

511
00:31:51,240 --> 00:31:52,840
and more maids risked their life.

512
00:31:54,840 --> 00:31:56,160
Nothing can deter the culprits

513
00:31:57,280 --> 00:31:58,840
other than punishing her seriously under the law.

514
00:32:03,440 --> 00:32:04,280
This night,

515
00:32:04,920 --> 00:32:06,200
you must be very tired.

516
00:32:07,040 --> 00:32:07,720
Have a seat now.

517
00:32:09,160 --> 00:32:11,080
We need to discuss about it.

518
00:32:12,920 --> 00:32:16,640
Yuan’s crime is clear.

519
00:32:17,360 --> 00:32:18,560
She’s not wronged.

520
00:32:19,960 --> 00:32:21,680
Now, everyone

521
00:32:21,960 --> 00:32:22,960
sees it.

522
00:32:24,320 --> 00:32:25,640
If you forgive her

523
00:32:26,360 --> 00:32:27,440
this time,

524
00:32:28,480 --> 00:32:30,920
I’m afraid it will be harder to control
the servants.

525
00:32:32,640 --> 00:32:34,600
Your Majesty please set store by overall interests.

526
00:32:35,160 --> 00:32:36,160
Sentence her to death

527
00:32:37,240 --> 00:32:38,520
immediately.

528
00:32:41,320 --> 00:32:42,120
Your Majesty,

529
00:32:42,320 --> 00:32:43,960
please save me.

530
00:32:44,440 --> 00:32:45,800
I‘m willing to get beaten.

531
00:32:45,960 --> 00:32:47,800
I have mother and sister at home.

532
00:32:48,360 --> 00:32:49,280
Please, Your Majesty.

533
00:32:51,720 --> 00:32:52,920
When colluding with Yan Xiu,

534
00:32:54,040 --> 00:32:57,160
you should have thought about
your mother and sister.

535
00:32:59,320 --> 00:33:00,280
Danshu, sit now.

536
00:33:00,440 --> 00:33:01,640
Let’s talk about

537
00:33:01,640 --> 00:33:02,760
how to punish her.

538
00:33:15,480 --> 00:33:16,200
Your Majesty.

539
00:33:17,200 --> 00:33:20,400
It’s almost the time of the morning meeting.

540
00:33:30,320 --> 00:33:30,920
OK.

541
00:33:33,920 --> 00:33:35,400
You decide how to punish her.

542
00:33:51,960 --> 00:33:53,760
With the weapon of rules,

543
00:33:53,760 --> 00:33:54,760
you are against me for your life.

544
00:33:56,800 --> 00:33:57,640
Cao Danshu,

545
00:33:59,760 --> 00:34:01,280
have you got what you want?

546
00:34:39,520 --> 00:34:40,840
Take Yuan Cailing out

547
00:34:42,080 --> 00:34:43,200
and execute her at East Yard.

548
00:34:44,520 --> 00:34:45,160
Yes.

549
00:35:00,760 --> 00:35:01,680
Imperial Security Agency

550
00:35:02,160 --> 00:35:04,760
keeps for arresting the culprits at full stretch.

551
00:35:06,560 --> 00:35:07,640
Don’t kill them.

552
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:10,520
Yes.

553
00:35:43,320 --> 00:35:44,240
You may go.

554
00:35:46,080 --> 00:35:47,120
Without my order,

555
00:35:48,240 --> 00:35:49,480
no one can enter.

556
00:36:46,720 --> 00:36:47,560
Your Highness.

557
00:36:58,480 --> 00:36:59,720
Why are you here?

558
00:37:03,960 --> 00:37:04,720
Your Highness.

559
00:37:05,360 --> 00:37:06,480
Time for breakfast.

560
00:37:13,840 --> 00:37:14,560
Qiuhe.

561
00:37:17,240 --> 00:37:18,920
You’ll go out of the palace in three days.

562
00:37:21,600 --> 00:37:22,280
Well,

563
00:37:23,920 --> 00:37:25,080
I’ll send you out

564
00:37:27,440 --> 00:37:28,920
to collect some spice.

565
00:37:34,160 --> 00:37:34,880
Your Highness.

566
00:37:35,720 --> 00:37:37,160
Your Highness, don’t worry.

567
00:37:38,200 --> 00:37:39,920
His Majesty will protect you

568
00:37:40,720 --> 00:37:42,480
and people around you.

569
00:37:56,560 --> 00:37:57,520
Protect me?

570
00:38:01,320 --> 00:38:02,080
Your Highness.

571
00:38:04,120 --> 00:38:06,240
His Majesty is always protecting you.

572
00:38:11,760 --> 00:38:12,640
What?

573
00:38:16,560 --> 00:38:18,760
When Deputy Officer Yang

574
00:38:19,520 --> 00:38:21,200
showed Ling’er’s parcel,

575
00:38:22,040 --> 00:38:23,320
I was shocked.

576
00:38:24,640 --> 00:38:27,200
Ling’er had admitted

577
00:38:27,200 --> 00:38:28,400
her affair with Yan Xiu.

578
00:38:29,120 --> 00:38:31,440
If someone fabricated the evidence

579
00:38:31,440 --> 00:38:32,840
in that parcel

580
00:38:33,600 --> 00:38:36,120
that she took part in treason

581
00:38:36,840 --> 00:38:38,160
and made you involved,

582
00:38:39,520 --> 00:38:41,360
how can you explain?

583
00:38:42,880 --> 00:38:45,320
His Majesty ordered to burn
that parcel immediately,

584
00:38:46,240 --> 00:38:49,080
and obviously he protected you.

585
00:38:54,880 --> 00:38:55,760
I think

586
00:38:58,080 --> 00:39:00,360
he spoke for Ling’er

587
00:39:01,520 --> 00:39:02,920
not because he was muddled

588
00:39:04,360 --> 00:39:06,640
or he didn’t know

589
00:39:07,040 --> 00:39:07,880
that others would imitate her

590
00:39:07,880 --> 00:39:08,920
and frame you up,

591
00:39:10,520 --> 00:39:11,400
but because

592
00:39:15,520 --> 00:39:18,120
he was confident to control this matter.

593
00:39:20,560 --> 00:39:24,400
His Majesty also knows

594
00:39:26,160 --> 00:39:30,000
that you are softhearted.

595
00:39:31,840 --> 00:39:33,400
He doesn’t want you to be

596
00:39:33,560 --> 00:39:35,160
a ruthless one in others’ words.

597
00:39:36,160 --> 00:39:37,880
He knows you will be grieved for it.

598
00:39:44,240 --> 00:39:45,120
Qiuhe.

599
00:39:50,120 --> 00:39:51,200
I also don’t know

600
00:39:55,960 --> 00:39:58,040
how I got here.

601
00:40:01,960 --> 00:40:03,600
I married the best

602
00:40:05,480 --> 00:40:07,920
and my favorite man.

603
00:40:11,680 --> 00:40:13,400
Though he doesn’t like me,

604
00:40:17,120 --> 00:40:18,640
my heart is for him.

605
00:40:24,760 --> 00:40:26,320
I want to take care of him.

606
00:40:33,160 --> 00:40:34,400
I want to help him.

607
00:40:39,720 --> 00:40:42,520
I don’t want to bring any trouble for him.

608
00:40:47,760 --> 00:40:48,520
So

609
00:40:49,920 --> 00:40:50,680
though I can’t be his loved one,

610
00:40:50,680 --> 00:40:52,480
I think I can

611
00:40:56,640 --> 00:40:58,880
be his good wife.

612
00:41:02,560 --> 00:41:03,240
At...

613
00:41:03,760 --> 00:41:07,000
At least, we can respect

614
00:41:08,120 --> 00:41:09,520
and treat each other well.

615
00:41:15,920 --> 00:41:16,880
Why...

616
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:24,520
Why are we always like this?

617
00:41:33,120 --> 00:41:34,760
I mean no offense,

618
00:41:35,440 --> 00:41:36,400
but I want to say something.

619
00:41:36,720 --> 00:41:38,200
Punish me if I’m wrong.

620
00:41:38,520 --> 00:41:39,880
Please don’t be angry.

621
00:41:42,400 --> 00:41:43,960
Your Highness, you don’t just want

622
00:41:45,240 --> 00:41:46,960
to be His Majesty’s good wife

623
00:41:48,080 --> 00:41:49,280
and live a calm life with him.

624
00:41:54,640 --> 00:41:57,720
You want to be his loved one,

625
00:41:58,960 --> 00:42:00,040
the only one.

626
00:42:01,960 --> 00:42:02,920
But

627
00:42:05,000 --> 00:42:07,440
you don’t think you can

628
00:42:08,560 --> 00:42:09,360
or you should

629
00:42:09,920 --> 00:42:11,040
get his love.

630
00:42:12,440 --> 00:42:13,200
So

631
00:42:16,760 --> 00:42:19,280
you don’t dare to admit it

632
00:42:21,240 --> 00:42:25,520
or let His Majesty know.

633
00:42:42,210 --> 00:42:49,210
♪ Memory is the breath of deep sleep ♪

634
00:42:49,770 --> 00:42:56,650
♪ It emerges in every crevice ♪

635
00:42:57,130 --> 00:43:03,490
♪ Shallow dreams are like
copper bells under eaves ♪

636
00:43:03,930 --> 00:43:10,690
♪ Woken up when the wind blows ♪

637
00:43:11,930 --> 00:43:18,730
♪ Fate is predetermined ♪

638
00:43:19,330 --> 00:43:26,090
♪ Struggle to break out of it ♪

639
00:43:26,650 --> 00:43:33,690
♪ Who will battle fate with me ♪

640
00:43:33,690 --> 00:43:40,490
♪ Regardless of the ending ♪

641
00:43:45,370 --> 00:43:48,890
♪ Peach branches shake in the spring breeze ♪

642
00:43:49,090 --> 00:43:52,690
♪ Walls sigh, the wind is silent ♪

643
00:43:52,690 --> 00:43:55,890
♪ The boy beside the wall is unaware of it ♪

644
00:43:55,890 --> 00:44:00,290
♪ He plays with the butterfly, gathering honey ♪

645
